{
  "stem": "13251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's the only-- the only-- in other words, I always go back to, from what I heard as a child, is Germany, which was like America.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was like the best place to live at one time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people were-- were very, very happy there, proud to be Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, they were dragged to the concentration camps, and they were screaming, I'm a Deutsche, you know, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm German, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- and-- I want Americans not to forget that, you know, saying they're American, huh.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could happen anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If-- if the-- the climate is right, human nature is very-- [LAUGHS] is not stable, let me put it that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It could be-- could be swayed and-- and influenced to do almost anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, that's what history, even though it doesn't make sense, has happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if it happens in-- in a-- in-- in a society that's intellectually-- I mean, the Germans, let's face it, there's no more intellects than the German society.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if it happened there, it could happen anywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just remembering that it could happen, remembering it's a possibility.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not saying it couldn't happen again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's not true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to be-- to be alert to the signs of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Could happen elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the only way can avoid it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know if that's the same thing as do like the atomic warfare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As long as we know it's out there and it's a threat, we're not doing it, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So that's the way I think-- as long as people are consciously aware it could happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's why, I guess, we try to keep this-- this-- the past alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's not forgotten.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
